> ***Dreadful Breath (Recharge 5-6).*** The proto-dragon exhales sludge in a 60-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC 16 Dexterity saving throw, taking 40 (9d8) poison damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. A creature that fails their saving throw by 5 or more must make a DC 15 Constitution save or contract the plague of undeath.
> 
> ***Wing Buffet (Recharge 5-6).*** The proto-dragon beats its wings with fury. Each creature within 10 feet of it must succeed on a DC 17 Dexterity saving throw or take 12 (2d6 + 5) bludgeoning damage and be knocked prone.

